The example is not the best one. After merging in #56 I think I'll make something more spectacular - indexing local text files would be the best option I guess, or indexing different Wikipedia articles / doing local search - or something like this.

@grabbou check the idea I had for switching the backend. I guess per-module global variable as a driver is not the best option, maybe you'd suggest other way handling it - feel free

The cool thing is that in this implementation we're dependency free (for the in-memory vector store) so it can be even moved to the core
